'''Homerus''' (Yunani Kuno: {{Polytonic|[[wikt:Ὅμηρος#Ancient_Greek|Ὅμηρος]]}}, ''Hómēros'') marupokan saurang penyair legendaris pado maso Yunani Kuno, diantaro karyanyo adolah ''Iliad'' dan ''Odyssey''. Sacaro umum dalam sejarah Yunani Kuno, Homerus ko memang pernah ado, walaupun kalangan sejarahwan kini masih maragukannyo<ref>G. S. Kirk's comment that "Antiquity knew nothing definite about the life and personality of Homer" represents the general consensus (Kirk, ''The Iliad: a Commentary'' (Cambridge 1985), v. 1).</ref> dan puisi nan ado tu hanyo marupokan kaba nan disampaikan sacaro turun temurun dari mulut ke mulut se salamo baabad-abad. Menurut [[Martin Litchfield West|Martin West]], "Homerus" ko hanyo saurang tokoh fiktif sajo.<ref>{{Cite journal|author= West, Martin|title=The Invention of Homer|journal=Classical Quarterly|volume=49|year=1999|issue=364}}</ref>

